divs: Sighting Detailsvery high wind gust caused me to go outside as i heard what sounded like a coverter box blow. was outside in front of my apartment looking aroud at the electric poles when I saw TWO BRIGHT LIGHTS FLYING IN AN -S- SHAPED PATTERN BEHIND EACH OTHER. started off as two seperate points of light in the sky. looked like they were either chasing eachother or flying in an S shaped pattern.. The first light then morphed into what looked like the top of a trident. outer edges were bluish and the center redish.. flew across the sky for approx. 2 min. I went inside to grab my camera phone, but object was gone.
